high_descs: Turn right, head around the kitchen to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the mug from the counter right of the stove.
Turn around and bring the mug to the fridge on the left.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine left of the fridge.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn to your right, then turn right again to enter the kitchen, and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the mug from the edge of the counter.
Turn around, and walk to the fridge on your left.
Cool the mug in the fridge, then pick it up again.
Turn around and walk to the coffee machine on your right.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then right again to stand in front of the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick the white mug up from the counter.
Go to the right and stand facing the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the mug on the top shelf, close the door and then open the door, and take the mug out and then shut the door.
Go to the left and stand in front of the counter in front of the blue coffee maker.
Put the mug down under the blue coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under a coffee maker.
